記"},{"pid":"e27a81771c79f518362ecfa645979aa943697c3b","tid":21324,"uid":1433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T20:53:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>是這樣子<br />\n本人練習倉頡已久<br />\n毫無進步<br />\n打速成太慢<br />\n所以平常都用漢語拼音<br />\n但在這裏用書面語感覺很奇怪<br />\n因爲很多粵語字不能打出來<br />\n怎辦呢？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都係用蝗語拼音（我都覺得自己柒但真係打慣左太快改好難改），粵字係一定出到，你有心機查就得。"},{"pid":"3fe88298b77ce447737e67b24e101b788dd6833f","tid":21324,"uid":41388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T20:56:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中學個陣唔識打字用手寫版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 無錢買個新唯有學速成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8b44da98cd8e62710f2082f1884002889f11785","tid":21324,"uid":33694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T21:22:59.000Z","msg":"電話筆畫<br />\n電腦用google 粵語拼音"},{"pid":"3b6c8b54030def07e5ae1c699d75cdb78b048e7c","tid":21324,"uid":8935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T21:56:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>九方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n九方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n <br />\n九方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n九方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ebca2dd453202e72cd1d585c635d6a57eafb72b","tid":21324,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T22:50:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>是這樣子<br />\n本人練習倉頡已久<br />\n毫無進步<br />\n打速成太慢